{"tid":245601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一個人衰到咩程度先可以中雀屎","createTime":"2017-05-16T11:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T16:42:47.000Z","uid":74459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b20d9e1f9fba48ef8f28a7b68f359cbc67fba261","tid":245601,"uid":74459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"排緊隊準備上車翻屋企<br />\n突然feel到好似有滴野滴左係膊頭<br />\n好自然摸一摸<br />\n屌你老母啡綠色！？<br />\n即刻搵紙巾抹<br />\n痴晒係頭髮到好似抹極都仲有咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廿幾歲女都冇做過咩壞事姐點解咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者一個人好彩到咩程度先可以見到你前面個人中雀屎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忍唔住周圍望下好似冇人見到<br />\n但為咗唔好太柒我都唯有扮冇野<br />\n依家落埋車行到屋企樓下都仲未接受到<br />\n翻到去即刻沖涼<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93a9f34f4aec67dd9d4653f0996637214971844","tid":245601,"uid":28190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:13:33.000Z","msg":"中頭獎代表好運"},{"pid":"d71907b0eb31b92a64e5f8ddf50e5731718f4fad","tid":245601,"uid":5921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:16:20.000Z","msg":"試過中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff5764e6b1bcc4cb47dab9590f8b57c2d491043","tid":245601,"uid":54755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:17:54.000Z","msg":"中學果陣試過一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母啡綠色！？呢句笑到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f1f8aa5b1d1b9e5e48c273cd9d58997a1222a1","t